    <description lang="en">
    <![CDATA[
bbDKP for phpBB3 brings together the DKP management facilites of EQdkp and 
integrates them fully with phpBB3's facilities.  This means your users gain single 
sign on to dkp, and you gain a clean interface, robust admin facilities and less headaches. 
Games supported : Aion, Daoc, Eq, Eq2, ffxi, lotro, vanguard, warhammer, Wow. 
Features : Multiple Dkp Pools, Multiple Guilds, Standings, Raids, Events, Item values, Item history, Raid Stats, Bossprogress, Roster, backup, import from Eqdkp.
Available Plugins : 
•	Armory Import (Wow & Aion), 
•	bbTips (Wow), 
•	Ct_Raidtracker (wow), 
•	Recruitment (Wow).  

As of the current release, it does not (yet) make coffee ;)

Minimum Requirements : 
phpBB3 v3.0.x, PHP 5.1.0 and Libxml 2.6.0 (simplexml usage) 
Mysql 4.1 (subqueries & utf-8) or Oracle, MSSQL, Postgresql
Curl (connectivity) 
Disclaimer : bbdkp is in release candidate stage but not yet final. 
Please Backup your phpbb3 installation and database before beginning. 
Further development requests, support questions are welcome at http://www.bbdkp.com

